10
00:02:23,419 --> 00:02:26,560
Scored the music through the night
밤새도록 음악을 만들었어.

11
00:02:28,819 --> 00:02:31,199
The folder grows the version climbs
폴더는 커지고, 버전은 올라가고.

12
00:02:33,420 --> 00:02:36,159
